cars.description: Acceleration, horsepower, fuel efficiency, weight, and other characteristics of different makes and models of cars. This dataset was originally published by Donoho et al (1982) [1]_, and was made public at http://lib.stat.cmu.edu/datasets/
references: Donoho, David and Ramos, Ernesto (1982), ``PRIMDATA:  Data Sets for Use With PRIM-H'' (DRAFT).
